definitions.definition: Someone who or something that moves .
A person employed to help people move their possessions from one residence to another.
examples: I'm getting too old to expect my friends to schlep all my stuff for beer and pizza. I'm hiring movers this time.

definitions.definition: Someone who proposes a motion at a meeting.
A chess problem in which the solver must attain checkmate within the specified number of moves.
